{"tid":294998,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"4月新番】 劍姬神聖譚 11","createTime":"2017-06-23T12:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T19:01:59.000Z","uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9c112bcf3abf3f77ccb8a86a73bf0f3fa785ee","tid":294998,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fGRSpYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfGRSpYr.jpg&h=d01488a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正傳只有149句台詞的【劍姬】艾絲&middot;華倫斯坦。<br />\n以最強聞名的女劍士今天也和同伴們一起，<br />\n前往廣大的地下迷宮「地下城」。<br />\n腐朽成灰的龍的殘骸，隱藏於暗處的異常事態<br />\n在種種神秘的威脅來襲的深層域50階層，<br />\n艾絲呼喚疾風，在迷宮的黑暗中刻下一閃！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;之後來訪的是，與少年的「邂逅」<br />\n「那個&hellip;&hellip;你，沒事嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n在迷宮都市歐拉麗之地，<br />\n少女與少年的物語鮮烈地交錯！<br />\n<br />\n這是，另一個眷族的物語，<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;【劍姬神聖譚Sword Oratoria】&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：大森藤ノ<br />\n角色原案：灰村清孝、安田典生<br />\n監督：鈴木洋平<br />\n系列構成：白根秀樹<br />\n角色設計：木本茂樹<br />\n音樂：井內啟二<br />\n動畫製作：J.C.STAFF<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n艾絲&middot;華倫斯坦:大西沙織<br />\n蕾菲亞&middot;維里迪斯:木村珠莉<br />\n蒂奧娜&middot;席呂特:村川梨衣<br />\n蒂奧涅&middot;席呂特:高橋未奈美<br />\n洛基:久保由利香<br />\n芬恩&middot;蒂姆那:田村睦心<br />\n里維莉雅&middot;利歐斯&middot;阿爾弗:川澄綾子(正傳動畫版:種田梨沙)<br />\n貝爾&middot;克朗尼：松岡禎丞<br />\n赫斯緹雅：水瀨祈<br />\nviu逢星期五深夜 03:30更新"},{"pid":"3027bed9c34dad99e40c492265b04b70e4dff7ed","tid":294998,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T12:04:41.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"73eeea63e95e4cd39b2d94213aef63d3195d1d68","tid":294998,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T12:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/200513_b4128812f4d7f4683ed04e69bf478c36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F200513_b4128812f4d7f4683ed04e69bf478c36.jpg&h=f61e2f07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df394380e5452abd57abc2fb5a762663ff6f412a","tid